('Tejada Solicitors', 'Legal', 'English-speaking law firm based in Malaga (Costa del Sol) with over 15 years of experience serving expats and international clients. Family-run business specializing in property conveyancing, Spanish residency and visas (Digital Nomad, Non-Lucrative, Golden Visa), tax advice for residents and non-residents, inheritance law, and last wills. Multi-disciplinary team includes lawyers, economists, tax consultants, and architects. Services available across Costa del Sol including Malaga city, Marbella, Mijas, Fuengirola, Benalmadena, Torremolinos, Nerja, Vélez-Málaga, Torrox and Torre del Mar. Members of Colegio de Abogados de Malaga, Colegio de Economistas de Malaga, Colegio de Arquitectos de Malaga, and British Chamber of Commerce in Spain. Power of attorney services available for clients abroad.', 'C/ Camino de Málaga, 22 1ºC', 'Vélez-Málaga', 'Málaga', '+34 676 81 52 62', 'info@tejadasolicitors.com', 'https://tejadasolicitors.com', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
